{"tid":1295751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動要成功一定要擊中要害","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T13:42:50.000Z","uid":275238,"like":23,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e012eb586b339eb448e03090c6c3365384c75439","tid":1295751,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"個個禮拜去埋晒啲無謂地方示威遊行根本冇撚用，政府同林鄭只會當係嘉年華，望都廢撚事<br />\n<br />\n政府個要害唔係乜野立法會，警總，甚至政總都唔係，而係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">禮賓府</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個個禮拜去禮賓府<strong>拜訪</strong>下林鄭，日日同佢搞下禮賓府開放日，日夜疲勞轟炸煩撚到林鄭仆街，佢自然就會回應訴求，正如收數佬日日係債仔樓下等佢，晩晩打電話俾佢，就算個債仔幾硬淨都會有日頂唔順投降<br />\n<br />\n話我係p牌，係鬼，分化撚，是撚但你地，我講嘅嘢自己諗下啱唔啱"},{"pid":"8cf4721b41cfa931fe9917f95c2bf592948ec849","tid":1295751,"uid":275238,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"依家遊行越遊越失焦點，越來越少人講5大訴求，未來只會越遊越少人，最後好似佔中咁玩撚完<br />\n<br />\n打要打要害，擒賊先擒王<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學明智光秀話齋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">敵人就在禮賓府！！！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"55da4a1542520e0a6132ae6cb764f7bb8519951a","tid":1295751,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人就在禮賓府！！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d87fdb2846c591bb11cb2eafab0e2faf7e50d033","tid":1295751,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人就在禮賓府！！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1226000c01c91267f49d3501bfe294687c24dc39","tid":1295751,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:46:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295342/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295342/page/1</a><br />\n[英文速譯] 綜合大量警察嚴重違規行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2de7df28cdff8fa9d300c728c4d3440f84e264